    </div>
    <div class="h-full pb-24">
      <div
        class="text-lg lg:text-2xl pb-2 lg:pb-4 uppercase tracking-wide font-normal text-center lg:text-left"
      >
        Can't Adopt?
      </div>
      <div
        class="text-4xl lg:text-7xl font-semibold text-center lg:text-left uppercase tracking-wide mb-4 lg:mb-8"
      >
        Sponsorables
      </div>
      <p class="text-base lg:text-2xl text-left lg:mx-0 mx-4">
        Try sponsoring! Call one of our permanent residents your own and learn
